---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = 'FUSA Damascus · Selected work · Rekraft Design';
const description = 'Premium Damascus chef-knife brand. Astro single-product editorial site, scroll-scrubbed Higgs Field rotation hero, cook-first copy. Case study by Rekraft Design.';
const canonical = 'https://rekraft.design/work/fusa-kitchen';
---

<Base title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Nav />
  <main class="case">
    <div class="frame case-back-wrap">
      <a href="/#work" class="case-back font-mono">&larr; Selected Work</a>
    </div>

    <section class="section case-intro">
      <div class="frame">
        <header class="case-head">
          <span class="eyebrow">Case Study &middot; 02 &middot; Knives</span>
          <h1 class="display-1 reveal-words" data-hero-headline>
            FUSA Damascus. <em class="italic-accent">The one knife.</em>
          </h1>
          <p class="lead fade-up">
            Premium Damascus chef-knife brand. A single-product Astro site centred on the Kiritsuke, a scroll-scrubbed Higgs Field rotation hero, and copy rewritten for cooks instead of forge nerds.
          </p>
          <a href="https://fusa-kitchen.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary case-cta-link fade-up">
            Visit the live site <span class="case-arrow-up">&#8599;</span>
          </a>
        </header>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="case-meta-strip">
      <div class="frame case-meta-inner font-mono">
        <span><b>Industry</b> &middot; Premium kitchen goods</span>
        <span><b>Location</b> &middot; London</span>
        <span><b>Scope</b> &middot; Brand + website + AI motion</span>
        <span><b>Live</b> &middot; May 2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="case-showcase">
      <div class="frame">
        <div class="case-browser fade-up">
          <div class="case-browser-bar">
            <div class="case-browser-dots">
              <span></span><span></span><span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="case-browser-url font-mono"><b>fusa-kitchen.vercel.app</b></div>
          </div>
          <iframe
            class="case-browser-frame"
            src="https://fusa-kitchen.vercel.app"
            title="Fusa Kitchen - live website"
            loading="lazy"
            sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups"
          ></iframe>
          <a class="case-browser-open" href="https://fusa-kitchen.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Open live site in a new tab">
            <span>Open live site &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-block">
      <div class="frame">
        <div class="case-split">
          <div class="case-split-text fade-up">
            <span class="eyebrow">Cinematic by scroll</span>
            <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
              The knife <em class="italic-accent">rotates as you read.</em>
            </h2>
            <p>The hero is a Higgs Field-generated rotation video of the Kiritsuke rolling around its own long axis. Scroll position scrubs the video timeline frame-by-frame, so the knife is anchored horizontal in frame and rolls from the underside Damascus pattern up to the iconic top face by 40% of hero scroll. Encoded with dense keyframes for jank-free seek on Safari. Mobile and reduced-motion users get a static photo with a light-rake reveal instead, because direct video scrub on iOS drops frames.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="case-phone fade-up" data-d="1">
            <iframe
              class="case-phone-frame"
              src="https://fusa-kitchen.vercel.app"
              title="Fusa Kitchen - mobile view"
              loading="lazy"
              sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-block">
      <div class="frame">
        <header class="case-block-head fade-up">
          <span class="eyebrow">What it delivers</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            Built to <em class="italic-accent">match the knife.</em>
          </h2>
        </header>
        <ol class="case-list">
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">01</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">A brand world, not a template</h3>
            <p>Every visual decision was made specifically for FUSA. The colour, the type, the rhythm of the page, the way photography sits on the screen. Visitors land on a brand they recognise on sight, not a wrapper around a product.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">02</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">A hero that stops the scroll</h3>
            <p>The Kiritsuke rotates as you scroll, Damascus pattern catching warm light from every angle. Product photography turned into a moment of motion. The knife is the centrepiece, and visitors notice. The story, the spec, and the price all wait until you have seen the work.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">03</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">Copy that sounds like the cook</h3>
            <p>The page speaks to the cook reading it, not the maker writing it. Less forge romance, more honest utility. Cooks read the page, recognise themselves in it, and trust the product. That is how a premium knife earns the price on the tag.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-stats-section">
      <div class="frame">
        <ul class="case-stats">
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>1</em> hero knife</div>
            <p>The Kiritsuke, anchored as the brand. Gyuto, Cleaver, and Deba live on the secondary collection page.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up" data-d="1">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>67</em> layers</div>
            <p>VG-10 core wrapped in 67 alternating layers of soft and high-carbon steel. The number stretches to 280px on desktop and counts up from zero as you scroll past.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up" data-d="2">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>0</em> shared tokens</div>
            <p>Not a single colour, font, or component is shared with rekraft.design. The portfolio brief was independence and the build proves it.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-cta">
      <div class="frame">
        <div class="case-cta-inner">
          <span class="eyebrow">Next case study</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            Want to be <em class="italic-accent">next?</em>
          </h2>
          <p class="lead fade-up">
            We take on a small number of bespoke projects each quarter. If you have something serious to build, let's talk.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:mark@rekraft.design?subject=Project%20Enquiry" class="btn btn-primary case-cta-btn fade-up">
            Start a conversation <span class="case-arrow-up">&#8599;</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/#work" class="case-back-bottom font-mono">&larr; All selected work</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  /* Back link */
  .case-back-wrap { padding-top: clamp(96px, 12vw, 140px); }
  .case-back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color .35s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-back:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }

  /* Hero */
  .case-intro { padding-block: clamp(32px, 4vw, 56px) clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px); }
  .case-head { display: grid; gap: 24px; max-width: 1080px; }
  .case-cta-link { justify-self: start; margin-top: 8px; }
  .case-arrow-up { display: inline-block; transition: transform .4s var(--ease-out-expo); }
  .btn:hover .case-arrow-up { transform: translate(3px, -3px); }

  /* Meta strip */
  .case-meta-strip {
    border-block: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding-block: 16px;
  }
  .case-meta-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(16px, 3vw, 36px);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
  }
  .case-meta-inner b {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }

  /* Browser iframe showcase — the centrepiece */
  .case-showcase { padding-block: clamp(56px, 8vw, 100px) clamp(24px, 4vw, 48px); }
  .case-browser {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-active);
    background: #0A0A0C;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 120px -40px rgba(20, 20, 24, 0.45);
    transition: border-color .35s var(--ease-out-expo), transform .35s var(--ease-out-expo), box-shadow .35s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-browser:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-lime);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 50px 150px -40px rgba(20, 20, 24, 0.55);
  }
  .case-browser-open {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 22px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .case-browser-open span {
    pointer-events: auto;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-active);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(6px);
    transition: opacity .35s var(--ease-out-expo), transform .35s var(--ease-out-expo);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .case-browser:hover .case-browser-open span {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .case-browser-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: #1A1A1D;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2A2A2E;
  }
  .case-browser-dots { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
  .case-browser-dots span {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #3A3A40;
  }
  .case-browser-dots span:nth-child(1) { background: #FF5F57; }
  .case-browser-dots span:nth-child(2) { background: #FEBC2E; }
  .case-browser-dots span:nth-child(3) { background: #28C840; }
  .case-browser-url {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    background: #0C0C0E;
    border: 1px solid #2A2A2E;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(245, 240, 229, 0.6);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .case-browser-url b { color: #F5F0E5; font-weight: 400; }
  .case-browser-frame {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    border: 0;
    display: block;
    background: #0E0E10;
  }

  /* Split: copy + phone iframe */
  .case-block {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-block: clamp(56px, 6vw, 88px);
  }
  .case-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(48px, 8vw, 120px);
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .case-split-text { display: grid; gap: 18px; }
  .case-split-text h2 { color: var(--color-ink); }
  .case-split-text p {
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 0.6vw + 12px, 18px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 56ch;
  }
  .case-phone {
    position: relative;
    width: 300px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 19.5;
    border-radius: 38px;
    padding: 14px;
    background: #1A1A1D;
    border: 1px solid #2A2A2E;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px -30px rgba(20, 20, 24, 0.45);
  }
  .case-phone::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 100px;
    height: 22px;
    background: #0A0A0C;
    border-radius: 14px;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .case-phone-frame {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 26px;
    display: block;
    background: #0E0E10;
  }

  /* What we built — numbered list (reused pattern) */
  .case-block-head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: clamp(28px, 3vw, 48px);
  }
  .case-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .case-list li {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 36px) 0;
    padding-left: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 40px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    column-gap: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px);
    row-gap: 14px;
    align-items: baseline;
    transition: background .5s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-list li:hover { background: var(--color-surface); }
  .case-list-num {
    grid-row: span 2;
    color: var(--color-lime);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .case-list h3 { color: var(--color-ink); }
  .case-list p {
    grid-column: 2;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 0.6vw + 12px, 18px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  /* Live-now stats */
  .case-stats-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-block: clamp(56px, 6vw, 88px);
  }
  .case-stats {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 40px);
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .case-stats li {
    padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--color-card);
    transition: border-color .25s var(--ease-out-expo), transform .25s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-stats li:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-active);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .case-stat-k {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: block;
  }
  .case-stat-big {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 2.4vw + 16px, 44px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .case-stat-big em {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .case-stats li p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* Bottom CTA */
  .case-cta {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .case-cta-inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    justify-items: center;
  }
  .case-cta-inner .lead { max-width: 56ch; }
  .case-cta-btn { justify-self: center; }
  .case-back-bottom {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    transition: color .35s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-back-bottom:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .case-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .case-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .case-browser { border-radius: 10px; }
    .case-browser-frame { aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .case-list li { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; padding-left: 20px; }
    .case-list-num { grid-row: auto; padding-top: 0; }
    .case-list p { grid-column: 1; }
    .case-phone { display: none; }
    .case-browser-url { display: none; }
    .case-browser-frame { aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
  }
</style>
